001package org.biopax.paxtools.impl.level3;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.model.BioPAXElement;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.FragmentFeature;
005
006
007public class FragmentFeatureImpl extends EntityFeatureImpl implements FragmentFeature
008{
009        public FragmentFeatureImpl() {}
010        
011        @Override
012        public Class<? extends FragmentFeature> getModelInterface()
013        {
014                return FragmentFeature.class;
015        }
016
017        @Override
018        protected boolean semanticallyEquivalent(BioPAXElement element)
019        {
020                if(!(element instanceof FragmentFeature))
021                        return false;
022                else
023                        return super.atEquivalentLocation(((FragmentFeature) element));
024        }
025
026    @Override
027    public String toString()
028    {
029        return "Fragment:"+this.getFeatureLocation();
030    }
031}
